{"id":424,"ayahs":[{"number":44,"arabic":"تَحِيَّتُهُمْ يَوْمَ يَلْقَوْنَهُۥ سَلَٰمٌۭ ۚ وَأَعَدَّ لَهُمْ أَجْرًۭا كَرِيمًۭا","translation":"On the Day when they meet Him, they will be welcomed with the greeting, “Peace”; and He will have readied for them a most excellent reward.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3577.mp3","surahId":33,"words":[{"id":44778,"position":1,"arabic":"تَحِيَّتُهُمْ","translation":"অভিবাদন (হবে)তাদের যেদিন","audioUrl":"wbw/033_044_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44779,"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"যে দিন","audioUrl":"wbw/033_044_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44780,"position":3,"arabic":"يَلْقَوْنَهُۥ","translation":"তারা সাক্ষাৎ করবে তাঁর সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_044_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44781,"position":4,"arabic":"سَلَـٰمٌۭ ۚ","translation":"সালাম (দিয়ে)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/033_044_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44783,"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَعَدَّ","translation":"এবং প্রস্তুত করে রেখেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/033_044_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44784,"position":6,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_044_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44785,"position":7,"arabic":"أَجْرًۭا","translation":"কর্মফল","audioUrl":"wbw/033_044_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44786,"position":8,"arabic":"كَرِيمًۭا","translation":"সম্মানজনক","audioUrl":"wbw/033_044_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44787,"position":9,"arabic":"٤٤","translation":"(৪৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":45,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّبِىُّ إِنَّآ أَرْسَلْنَٰكَ شَٰهِدًۭا وَمُبَشِّرًۭا وَنَذِيرًۭا","translation":"[And as for thee,] O Prophet - behold, We have sent thee as a witness [to the truth], and as a herald of glad tidings and a warner,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3578.mp3","surahId":33,"words":[{"id":45161,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_045_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45162,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِىُّ","translation":"নাবী","audioUrl":"wbw/033_045_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45163,"position":3,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/033_045_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45164,"position":4,"arabic":"أَرْسَلْنَـٰكَ","translation":"আমরা পাঠিয়েছি তোমাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_045_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45165,"position":5,"arabic":"شَـٰهِدًۭا","translation":"সাক্ষীরূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_045_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45166,"position":6,"arabic":"وَمُبَشِّرًۭا","translation":"এবং সুসংবাদদাতা","audioUrl":"wbw/033_045_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45167,"position":7,"arabic":"وَنَذِيرًۭا","translation":"ও সতর্ককারী হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_045_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45168,"position":8,"arabic":"٤٥","translation":"(৪৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":46,"arabic":"وَدَاعِيًا إِلَى ٱللَّهِ بِإِذْنِهِۦ وَسِرَاجًۭا مُّنِيرًۭا","translation":"and as one who summons [all men] to God by His leave, and as a light-giving beacon.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3579.mp3","surahId":33,"words":[{"id":46214,"position":1,"arabic":"وَدَاعِيًا","translation":"এবং আহবানকারীরূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_046_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46215,"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَى","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_046_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46216,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/033_046_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46217,"position":4,"arabic":"بِإِذْنِهِۦ","translation":"অনুসারে অনুমতি তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/033_046_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46218,"position":5,"arabic":"وَسِرَاجًۭا","translation":"ও প্রদীপস্বরূপ","audioUrl":"wbw/033_046_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46219,"position":6,"arabic":"مُّنِيرًۭا","translation":"উজ্জ্বল","audioUrl":"wbw/033_046_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46220,"position":7,"arabic":"٤٦","translation":"(৪৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":47,"arabic":"وَبَشِّرِ ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ بِأَنَّ لَهُم مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ فَضْلًۭا كَبِيرًۭا","translation":"And [so,] convey to the believers the glad tiding that a great bounty from God awaits them;","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3580.mp3","surahId":33,"words":[{"id":46843,"position":1,"arabic":"وَبَشِّرِ","translation":"এবং সুসংবাদ দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/033_047_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46844,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"মু'মিনদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_047_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46845,"position":3,"arabic":"بِأَنَّ","translation":"যে অবশ্যই","audioUrl":"wbw/033_047_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46846,"position":4,"arabic":"لَهُم","translation":"জন্যে (আছে)তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_047_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46847,"position":5,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"পক্ষ থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_047_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46848,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/033_047_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46849,"position":7,"arabic":"فَضْلًۭا","translation":"অনুগ্র্রহ","audioUrl":"wbw/033_047_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46850,"position":8,"arabic":"كَبِيرًۭا","translation":"বিরাট","audioUrl":"wbw/033_047_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46851,"position":9,"arabic":"٤٧","translation":"(৪৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":48,"arabic":"وَلَا تُطِعِ ٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ وَٱلْمُنَٰفِقِينَ وَدَعْ أَذَىٰهُمْ وَتَوَكَّلْ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ ۚ وَكَفَىٰ بِٱللَّهِ وَكِيلًۭا","translation":"and defer not to [the likes and dislikes of] the deniers of the truth and the hypocrites, and disregard their hurtful talk, and place thy trust in God: for none is as worthy of trust as God.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3581.mp3","surahId":33,"words":[{"id":47620,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47621,"position":2,"arabic":"تُطِعِ","translation":"আনুগত্য করো","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47622,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","translation":"কাফিরদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47623,"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُنَـٰفِقِينَ","translation":"ও মুনাফিকদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47624,"position":5,"arabic":"وَدَعْ","translation":"এবং উপেক্ষা করো","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47625,"position":6,"arabic":"أَذَىٰهُمْ","translation":"নির্যাতনকে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47626,"position":7,"arabic":"وَتَوَكَّلْ","translation":"এবং নির্ভর করো","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47627,"position":8,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47628,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ ۚ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47630,"position":10,"arabic":"وَكَفَىٰ","translation":"এবং যথেষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47631,"position":11,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহই","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47632,"position":12,"arabic":"وَكِيلًۭا","translation":"কর্মবিধায়ক হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_048_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47633,"position":13,"arabic":"٤٨","translation":"(৪৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":49,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓا۟ إِذَا نَكَحْتُمُ ٱلْمُؤْمِنَٰتِ ثُمَّ طَلَّقْتُمُوهُنَّ مِن قَبْلِ أَن تَمَسُّوهُنَّ فَمَا لَكُمْ عَلَيْهِنَّ مِنْ عِدَّةٍۢ تَعْتَدُّونَهَا ۖ فَمَتِّعُوهُنَّ وَسَرِّحُوهُنَّ سَرَاحًۭا جَمِيلًۭا","translation":"O YOU who have attained to faith! If you marry believing women and then divorce them ere you have touched them, you have no reason to expect, and to calculate, any waiting period on their part: hence, make [at once] provision for them, and release them in a becoming manner.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3582.mp3","surahId":33,"words":[{"id":47845,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47846,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47847,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوٓا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47848,"position":4,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47849,"position":5,"arabic":"نَكَحْتُمُ","translation":"তোমরা বিয়ে করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47850,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنَـٰتِ","translation":"মু’মিন নারীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47851,"position":7,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47852,"position":8,"arabic":"طَلَّقْتُمُوهُنَّ","translation":"তালাক দিবে তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47853,"position":9,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে (এর)","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47854,"position":10,"arabic":"قَبْلِ","translation":"পূর্বই","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47855,"position":11,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47856,"position":12,"arabic":"تَمَسُّوهُنَّ","translation":"তোমরা স্পর্শ করেছো তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47857,"position":13,"arabic":"فَمَا","translation":"তখন নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47858,"position":14,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47859,"position":15,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِنَّ","translation":"উপর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47860,"position":16,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47861,"position":17,"arabic":"عِدَّةٍۢ","translation":"ইদ্দত পালন","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47862,"position":18,"arabic":"تَعْتَدُّونَهَا ۖ","translation":"তোমরা গণনা করে থাকো যা","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47864,"position":19,"arabic":"فَمَتِّعُوهُنَّ","translation":"সুতরাং তোমরা ভোগ্যসামগ্রী দাও (কিছু) তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47865,"position":20,"arabic":"وَسَرِّحُوهُنَّ","translation":"এবং  বিদায় দাও তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47866,"position":21,"arabic":"سَرَاحًۭا","translation":"বিদায়","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47867,"position":22,"arabic":"جَمِيلًۭا","translation":"সৌজন্যের সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_049_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47868,"position":23,"arabic":"٤٩","translation":"(৪৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":50,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّبِىُّ إِنَّآ أَحْلَلْنَا لَكَ أَزْوَٰجَكَ ٱلَّٰتِىٓ ءَاتَيْتَ أُجُورَهُنَّ وَمَا مَلَكَتْ يَمِينُكَ مِمَّآ أَفَآءَ ٱللَّهُ عَلَيْكَ وَبَنَاتِ عَمِّكَ وَبَنَاتِ عَمَّٰتِكَ وَبَنَاتِ خَالِكَ وَبَنَاتِ خَٰلَٰتِكَ ٱلَّٰتِى هَاجَرْنَ مَعَكَ وَٱمْرَأَةًۭ مُّؤْمِنَةً إِن وَهَبَتْ نَفْسَهَا لِلنَّبِىِّ إِنْ أَرَادَ ٱلنَّبِىُّ أَن يَسْتَنكِحَهَا خَالِصَةًۭ لَّكَ مِن دُونِ ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ ۗ قَدْ عَلِمْنَا مَا فَرَضْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ فِىٓ أَزْوَٰجِهِمْ وَمَا مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَٰنُهُمْ لِكَيْلَا يَكُونَ عَلَيْكَ حَرَجٌۭ ۗ وَكَانَ ٱللَّهُ غَفُورًۭا رَّحِيمًۭا","translation":"O PROPHET! Behold, We have made lawful to thee thy wives unto whom thou hast paid their dowers, as well as those whom thy right hand has come to possess from among the captives of war whom God has bestowed upon thee. And [We have made lawful to thee] the daughters of thy paternal uncles and aunts, and the daughters of thy maternal uncles and aunts, who have migrated with thee [to Yathrib]; and any believing woman who offers herself freely to the Prophet and whom the Prophet might be willing to wed: [this latter being but] a privilege for thee, and not for other believers - [seeing that] We have already made known what We have enjoined upon them with regard to their wives and those whom their right hands may possess. [And] in order that thou be not burdened with [undue] anxiety - for God is indeed much-forgiving, a dispenser of grace –","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3583.mp3","surahId":33,"words":[{"id":48551,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_050_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48552,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِىُّ","translation":"নাবী","audioUrl":"wbw/033_050_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48553,"position":3,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/033_050_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48554,"position":4,"arabic":"أَحْلَلْنَا","translation":"বৈধ করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/033_050_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48555,"position":5,"arabic":"لَكَ","translation":"জন্যে তোমার","audioUrl":"wbw/033_050_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48556,"position":6,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجَكَ","translation":"স্ত্রীদেরকে তোমার","audioUrl":"wbw/033_050_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48557,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلَّـٰتِىٓ","translation":"যাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_050_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48558,"position":8,"arabic":"ءَاتَيْتَ","translation":"তুমি দিয়েছো","audioUrl":"wbw/033_050_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48559,"position":9,"arabic":"أُجُورَهُنَّ","translation":"মোহরগুলো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_050_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48560,"pos